PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of ROGER PLAMONDON, of St-Sauveur des Monts, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Guy Savard, whose term has expired.
